	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Scavenging</h1>
	
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From The Cataclysm: Dark Days Ahead Wiki</div>
		<div id="contentSub"><div class="mw-revision"><div id="mw-revision-info">Revision as of 05:21, 3 December 2021 by <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=User:Mrstickman1997&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new mw-userlink" title="User:Mrstickman1997 (page does not exist)"><bdi>Mrstickman1997</bdi></a> <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/User_talk:Mrstickman1997" class="mw-usertoollinks-talk" title="User talk:Mrstickman1997">talk</a> | <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Special:Contributions/Mrstickman1997" class="mw-usertoollinks-contribs" title="Special:Contributions/Mrstickman1997">contribs</a>)</span> <span class="comment">(<span dir="auto"><span class="autocomment"><a href="#Scavenging_for_guns_and_ammo">→‎Scavenging for guns and ammo</a>: </span> Added a little more in the way of tips.</span>)</span></div><div id="mw-revision-nav">(<a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Scavenging&amp;diff=prev&amp;oldid=40114" title="Scavenging">diff</a>) <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Scavenging&amp;direction=prev&amp;oldid=40114" title="Scavenging">← Older revision</a> | Latest revision (diff) | Newer revision → (diff)</div></div></div>
		
		
		
